attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a wheeled cart. They start by putting together the side bars and the base frame, then screwing the side bars onto the frame. Next, they insert the bottom tray and put together the brackets for the bottom tray. After that, they insert the middle and top trays, aligning the top tray. Finally, they assemble the wheels.
